As a player, 
when I select the paths between houses and click on validate, 
I should get a response on the UI indicating whether my path was the shortest or not #UserStories

Contract:

interface PathSetter{
  public boolean IsShortesPath(List<Path> SelectedPath);

  public Collection GetShortestPath(List<Path> AllPaths);
  
}


Required:

Class path should contain x-y coordinates for starting point of a path and ending point of a path.
Class path should contain the two House objects that the path contains 
